01:42:18,297 --> 01:42:20,288
''Open your mouth.
- Yes, son. Eat it.''

37
01:42:23,702 --> 01:42:25,294
But this action will
bring you disgrace.

38
01:42:27,306 --> 01:42:28,967
''l want Vaidehi, at any cost!''

39
01:42:29,308 --> 01:42:30,798
All the newspapers in this area..

40
01:42:32,311 --> 01:42:35,303
Print this photo in all.
The informer gets 100000 reward.

41
01:42:37,316 --> 01:42:38,977
What month?

42
01:42:39,652 --> 01:42:41,984
Mr. Purushottam said you're pregnant.

43
01:42:42,721 --> 01:42:44,313
l'm in the second
month of my pregnancy.

44
01:42:46,325 --> 01:42:48,054
What are you looking for?
Symbols of marriage?

45
01:42:48,694 --> 01:42:50,093
l'm not yet married.

46
01:42:50,262 --> 01:42:51,593
But we'll be married next month.

47
01:42:52,765 --> 01:42:54,665
''Here, use this to wipe. Go on.''

48
01:42:57,269 --> 01:42:59,066
Hurry and get a packet of Panama.

49
01:42:59,271 --> 01:43:02,263
We've finished lunch.
Manish will want a smoke.

50
01:43:02,942 --> 01:43:04,273
Deliver my stuff home.

51
01:43:04,677 --> 01:43:05,336
l understand.
- Come...

52
01:43:06,278 --> 01:43:10,271
''You know Manish, the hero..
He's going to be my ...''

53
01:43:12,618 --> 01:43:14,017
Have you run away from home?

54
01:43:15,287 --> 01:43:17,118
Have you had a scrap with your man?

55
01:43:19,291 --> 01:43:21,282
Tiku said you had no bags.

56
01:43:21,694 --> 01:43:24,686
l too wondered how you wore
the same clothes after a bath.

57
01:43:25,631 --> 01:43:27,064
But don't you worry.
l'll give you a sari.

58
01:43:27,299 --> 01:43:29,290
No..it's not really...
- l have plenty of clothes.

59
01:43:29,635 --> 01:43:30,966
''Come home with me.
- No, l don't need..''

60
01:43:32,304 --> 01:43:34,636
Coming...
You stay here. l'll be back.

61
01:43:36,308 --> 01:43:38,071
Yes?

62
01:43:38,310 --> 01:43:39,800
Did you call me?
- Come in.

63
01:43:40,312 --> 01:43:41,745
l am already in.

64
01:43:43,315 --> 01:43:44,907
What do you think of this necklace?

65
01:43:45,317 --> 01:43:47,842
Exquisite. Beautiful.

66
01:43:48,254 --> 01:43:51,246
What a design!
Bought it for Lata?

67
01:43:52,925 --> 01:43:55,587
l often told you
don't address her thus.

68
01:43:55,928 --> 01:43:57,589
''What should l call her?
- Elder sister, silly girl.''

69
01:43:58,264 --> 01:44:01,756
Sister..?
- l got this made specially for you.

70
01:44:02,268 --> 01:44:07,262
Really? But l think there's
a lot of time for Rakhi!

71
01:44:08,941 --> 01:44:10,272
You play the fool all the time!

72
01:44:11,277 --> 01:44:13,268
''Mr. Purushottam, you fool around.''

73
01:44:14,280 --> 01:44:16,271
l've often told you
l don't approve of this.

74
01:44:16,615 --> 01:44:18,276
But you don't seem to understand.

75
01:44:18,617 --> 01:44:21,609
l do. My mind has understood.

76
01:44:22,288 --> 01:44:25,746
But here..how do l
convince my heart?

77
01:44:26,292 --> 01:44:27,725
You are all it wants.

78
01:44:27,893 --> 01:44:31,294
How do l convince my heart
which only wants Manish?

79
01:44:31,463 --> 01:44:32,794
You are a fool!

80
01:44:33,799 --> 01:44:37,291
On one hand you have me who
wants to give you all l have.

81
01:44:37,970 --> 01:44:39,301
And you reject me!

82
01:44:39,905 --> 01:44:42,897
And you side with him
who lives off you!

83
01:44:43,309 --> 01:44:44,799
The scavenging dog!
- That's enough.

84
01:44:45,044 --> 01:44:48,241
Stop it. l won't hear
a word against Manish.

85
01:44:48,747 --> 01:44:50,078
''However he is, he is mine.''

86
01:44:50,249 --> 01:44:51,580
He means everything to me.

87
01:44:51,984 --> 01:44:54,851
What a temper!
My employee growls at me!

88
01:44:55,254 --> 01:45:00,248
''Sweet pie, don't forget
you signed a contact with me.''

89
01:45:01,260 --> 01:45:03,751
Now you will have
to dance to my tune.

90
01:45:06,265 --> 01:45:07,926
Just Purushottam?
No respect...?

91
01:45:08,267 --> 01:45:09,598
Cut away.

92
01:45:09,935 --> 01:45:13,598
You were never great. Talk too
much and you won't remain a man!

93
01:45:13,939 --> 01:45:16,271
l am lightning.
l don't dance at anyone's tune.

94
01:45:16,675 --> 01:45:19,269
''ln fact, when l strike
your tunes go out of tune.''

95
01:45:20,279 --> 01:45:21,940
As for the contract...

96
01:45:22,281 --> 01:45:26,081
Someday l'll make a kite out of
it and fly it from your terrace.

97
01:45:26,285 --> 01:45:28,014
And you'll stand with the string.

98
01:45:33,559 --> 01:45:34,890
Come in..

99
01:45:39,031 --> 01:45:40,293
You have a nice home.

100
01:45:41,300 --> 01:45:43,700
''Hardly a home, more like a room.''

101
01:45:43,969 --> 01:45:45,300
We have to set up our home.

102
01:45:45,704 --> 01:45:47,228
l'm getting ready for it.

103
01:45:48,240 --> 01:45:49,901
l have so many saris.

104
01:45:53,912 --> 01:45:55,243
l have all of them.

105
01:45:55,581 --> 01:45:57,242
''Honest, l have every kind of sari.''

106
01:45:57,649 --> 01:45:59,913
''You have quite a collection.
- Sure, why not...''

107
01:46:00,252 --> 01:46:02,914
''Even if of the stage,
but l am a heroine.''

108
01:46:03,255 --> 01:46:04,586
l have to maintain.

109
01:46:05,591 --> 01:46:08,253
''By the way, if a couple of men
don't turn round to stare at me..''

110
01:46:08,761 --> 01:46:10,251
l can't sleep at night.

111
01:46:11,263 --> 01:46:12,662
Which sari...?

112
01:46:13,766 --> 01:46:15,097
Here...Wear this.

113
01:46:15,267 --> 01:46:17,929
''This!
- Yes, l bought it for Navratri.''

114
01:46:18,270 --> 01:46:20,261
''lt will suit you.
Come on, wear it.''

115
01:46:20,606 --> 01:46:21,937
You'll look like Karishma.

116
01:46:22,274 --> 01:46:24,606
That is nice but..
- What?

117
01:46:24,777 --> 01:46:28,110
You won't be sullied by
wearing my sari. Take this off.

118
01:46:28,280 --> 01:46:31,943
l'll wear it but you go there.

119
01:46:33,619 --> 01:46:35,052
You are so shy..?

120
01:46:36,288 --> 01:46:38,279
You want me to wear this?
Then please go.

121
01:46:40,292 --> 01:46:42,624
What...? What are you doing?

122
01:46:46,098 --> 01:46:47,224
l think the guy is sleeping.

123
01:46:48,233 --> 01:46:50,224
You can't make out
anything in 2 months.

124
01:46:50,969 --> 01:46:52,231
ls it your second month?

125
01:46:53,238 --> 01:46:55,229
Wow! Same name and same time!

126
01:46:55,574 --> 01:46:56,905
Give me five.

127
01:46:57,576 --> 01:47:00,238
''No way, Mr. Purushottam.
Janki and l'd already told you..''

128
01:47:00,746 --> 01:47:03,237
This would be our last
play for your company.

129
01:47:03,982 --> 01:47:06,041
Now you want us to
enact Valmiki's Ramayana!

130
01:47:07,986 --> 01:47:10,580
What can we do if you've signed
the contract and taken the money!

131
01:47:12,257 --> 01:47:14,054
''No, sir. We are going to Delhi.''

132
01:47:14,259 --> 01:47:16,591
''Sure, my son. Go with pleasure.''

133
01:47:17,262 --> 01:47:20,254
''Go to Delhi, Bombay.
ln fact go to Hollywood!''

134
01:47:21,266 --> 01:47:23,257
l want you to rise very high.

135
01:47:24,269 --> 01:47:28,262
And one day l will rest only
after you've gone right up.

136
01:47:29,942 --> 01:47:33,275
''But before you leave,
forget about me...''

137
01:47:34,279 --> 01:47:36,770
Take the blessings of the
Ultimate Male God Rama.

138
01:47:37,616 --> 01:47:40,779
Dumping the Ramayana
is the worst thing to do.

139
01:47:41,286 --> 01:47:42,947
Yes!
- Sir...

140
01:47:43,288 --> 01:47:46,018
You got this precious necklace
made for Janki with such love...

141
01:47:46,291 --> 01:47:47,553
Why did you return it?

142
01:47:48,227 --> 01:47:50,218
l returned it because...

143
01:47:50,562 --> 01:47:52,621
The heart you made in the necklace...

144
01:47:53,232 --> 01:47:56,565
''Like your brain, you left it empty.''

145
01:47:57,903 --> 01:48:02,237
Janki wants P & J carved in it.

146
01:48:03,242 --> 01:48:05,005
l'll carve it in red.

147
01:48:05,244 --> 01:48:06,734
That's great.

148
01:48:08,247 --> 01:48:09,737
P & J.

149
01:48:09,982 --> 01:48:11,244
l got that.

150
01:48:11,583 --> 01:48:13,050
You were saying...

151
01:48:14,253 --> 01:48:16,244
ls there...something
between you and Janki?

152
01:48:17,256 --> 01:48:18,985
My dear son...

153
01:48:19,925 --> 01:48:25,261
Some questions give peace
of mind when left unanswered.

154
01:48:26,265 --> 01:48:28,256
lf you want me to act in your play..

155
01:48:29,601 --> 01:48:31,262
Tell me the truth.

156
01:48:32,271 --> 01:48:34,262
What is the relation
between you and Janki?

157
01:48:35,274 --> 01:48:37,265
Son...my son..

158
01:48:47,953 --> 01:48:49,284
Does Manish love you?

159
01:48:51,290 --> 01:48:52,780
What's this if not love?

160
01:48:53,292 --> 01:48:54,953
He loves me a lot.

161
01:48:55,294 --> 01:48:56,955
We're getting married next month.

162
01:48:57,296 --> 01:48:58,786
Then we're going to Delhi.

163
01:48:59,298 --> 01:49:01,289
My hero has got a role in a serial.

164
01:49:03,302 --> 01:49:05,293
Then he will earn and l'll blow it.

165
01:49:06,305 --> 01:49:07,897
l mean l'll run the house.

166
01:49:12,978 --> 01:49:15,310
''Must be Tiku.
Come in, the door is open.''

167
01:49:16,315 --> 01:49:18,306
Tiku used to be a barber
now he's an actor.

168
01:49:18,650 --> 01:49:20,982
Matter of time.
- Sister...here's your stuff.

169
01:49:21,987 --> 01:49:23,818
And your change.
- Keep it.

170
01:49:24,656 --> 01:49:26,988
Aren't you going to
watch a film today?

171
01:49:27,326 --> 01:49:29,317
The film has changed.
- Which one is playing?

172
01:49:33,332 --> 01:49:35,323
''l am full of life.
Control your senses''

173
01:49:36,335 --> 01:49:38,326
''Don't glare at me!''

174
01:49:38,670 --> 01:49:41,332
What man? Get 3 tickets
Use my name. - Okay.

175
01:49:41,740 --> 01:49:43,731
''We'll all go. You, me
and Manish. What fun!''

176
01:49:47,279 --> 01:49:49,611
Do you drink?
- Yes.

177
01:49:51,283 --> 01:49:53,615
l try to give it up but can't.

178
01:49:54,620 --> 01:49:56,281
But this is harmful to the baby.

179
01:49:56,788 --> 01:49:59,086
l know that is why l've reduced
from half to a quarter bottle.

180
01:50:00,692 --> 01:50:03,286
The problem is..
l can't sleep at night.

181
01:50:04,296 --> 01:50:05,786
All kinds of worries badger me.

182
01:50:07,299 --> 01:50:08,766
How did you fall in this vice?

183
01:50:09,301 --> 01:50:10,734
Thanks to Purushottam.

184
01:50:11,303 --> 01:50:12,793
He wanted to make me a heroine.

185
01:50:13,305 --> 01:50:15,296
But the stage scared me.

186
01:50:16,308 --> 01:50:18,833
One day he tricked me into
drinking and pushed me on stage.

187
01:50:20,312 --> 01:50:22,712
l got over the fear of stage
but got hooked to this.

188
01:50:23,315 --> 01:50:24,907
Didn't your parents prohibit you?

189
01:50:25,317 --> 01:50:26,841
They passed away when l was little.

190
01:50:27,319 --> 01:50:28,877
l'm working here since l was a kid.

191
01:50:29,321 --> 01:50:31,983
Do you know all of us
artists live in this house.

192
01:50:32,324 --> 01:50:33,723
Even Manish?

193
01:50:33,992 --> 01:50:35,323
Downstairs.

194
01:50:36,328 --> 01:50:39,764
''That is why, sweet..
That is why l said..''

195
01:50:40,332 --> 01:50:44,132
lt's best not to know
the answers to some questions.

196
01:50:44,336 --> 01:50:47,271
You are lying!
- l'm lying?

197
01:50:47,939 --> 01:50:49,270
But the holy books don't lie.

198
01:50:50,609 --> 01:50:53,100
And the holy book
says in huge letters..

199
01:50:53,545 --> 01:50:56,070
The woman who crosses
the threshold of her home..

200
01:50:56,682 --> 01:50:59,276
The character of that
woman can't be trusted.

201
01:50:59,951 --> 01:51:01,282
''To top it, an artist.''

202
01:51:02,287 --> 01:51:07,281
The face that is caked in
make-up can never be loyal.

203
01:51:09,961 --> 01:51:11,292
What do you mean to imply?

204
01:51:12,297 --> 01:51:16,290
You are a good human being
and an even better artist.

205
01:51:16,768 --> 01:51:19,293
On going to Delhi will
you look after your career?

206
01:51:20,305 --> 01:51:21,636
Or look after the baby?

207
01:51:22,307 --> 01:51:24,969
And God knows whose child it is.

208
01:51:31,316 --> 01:51:32,977
No!!!

209
01:51:35,320 --> 01:51:36,719
''Darling, what an entry!''

210
01:51:39,324 --> 01:51:40,916
Thrash them! Beat them all up!

211
01:51:41,326 --> 01:51:43,317
Beat them so much that they
rip the screen and fall here!

212
01:51:48,667 --> 01:51:49,998
You too must whistle.

213
