l can't.

214
01:51:53,271 --> 01:51:54,761
''Look, it's so easy.''

215
01:51:55,273 --> 01:51:56,672
Purse your lips together in style.

216
01:51:58,710 --> 01:52:00,268
And gently blow out.

217
01:52:02,013 --> 01:52:03,275
lsn't it simple?

218
