241
01:53:20,625 --> 01:53:22,616
Go and squat. l'll stand guard.

242
01:53:23,295 --> 01:53:27,629
Let's please go home.
- Do it or go home alone.

243
01:53:28,300 --> 01:53:30,291
You'll never advance in life.

244
01:53:30,702 --> 01:53:33,296
lf peeing on the road
helps one progress...

245
01:53:33,805 --> 01:53:35,295
l wonder where lndia
would have gone!

246
01:53:35,640 --> 01:53:36,971
And where are you!

247
01:53:37,309 --> 01:53:40,142
l'm at the stage where
l take my own decisions.

248
01:53:40,312 --> 01:53:41,711
lsn't that achievement enough?

249
01:53:42,314 --> 01:53:44,305
Now you decide.
Doing it or leaving?

250
01:53:44,716 --> 01:53:48,243
l'm going! l'll show you!
Now stand guard!

251
01:53:48,720 --> 01:53:51,245
Bravo! Spoken like a man!

252
01:53:58,263 --> 01:53:59,992
Doesn't the moon look lovely?

253
01:54:01,266 --> 01:54:03,029
lt relieves the eyes.

254
01:54:05,003 --> 01:54:06,595
lt grows by the day.

255
01:54:07,606 --> 01:54:09,267
And is complete one day.

256
01:54:10,275 --> 01:54:12,266
Our children too must be
growing up like this.

257
01:54:14,012 --> 01:54:15,274
One day they will take birth.

258
01:54:17,282 --> 01:54:18,749
l wonder where you will be.

259
01:54:19,618 --> 01:54:20,949
And where l will be.

260
01:54:22,954 --> 01:54:24,285
Will you think of me?

261
01:54:26,291 --> 01:54:27,952
l'll never forget you.

262
01:54:32,697 --> 01:54:36,292
''Like we have similar names,
let's give some name to our kids.''

263
01:54:36,368 --> 01:54:37,699
What do you say?

264
01:54:38,303 --> 01:54:39,770
''What do you want,
a son or a daughter?''

265
01:54:41,306 --> 01:54:43,774
''Considering my state,
l think it will be a boy.''

266
01:54:44,309 --> 01:54:45,776
The poor girl...

267
01:54:47,245 --> 01:54:48,906
Don't pity the girl.

268
01:54:50,248 --> 01:54:53,581
God filled girls with everything
in this universe that is good.

269
01:54:54,920 --> 01:54:58,583
''lf she wishes, she'll give
everyone a run for their money.''

270
01:54:59,257 --> 01:55:02,249
Whether it be God lndra
or the saint Vishwamitra.

271
01:55:02,761 --> 01:55:06,253
''Rambha, Urvashi and Menaka,
stop your stage acting.''

272
01:55:07,265 --> 01:55:08,926
Today l'll make you also dance.

273
01:55:09,267 --> 01:55:12,259
Come along. - Where?
- l have enough admirers.

274
01:55:54,245 --> 01:55:56,236
''Bangles, bangles..''

275
01:55:59,250 --> 01:56:01,241
''Ear rings, ear rings..''

276
01:56:05,256 --> 01:56:07,247
''Anklets...''

277
01:56:10,261 --> 01:56:12,252
''Bangles, bangles..''

278
