456
02:10:33,324 --> 02:10:34,313
Tell me...

457
02:10:35,326 --> 02:10:37,123
Are you with me or not?

458
02:10:38,696 --> 02:10:41,392
Answer me. Go on...

459
02:10:41,732 --> 02:10:44,326
Prompt her fast. She's
saying the wrong dialogues.

460
