Shame on Purushottam!!

527
02:15:21,278 --> 02:15:24,076
Down with Janki! Shame!

528
02:15:24,481 --> 02:15:27,279
Shame on Purushottam!!

529
02:15:33,056 --> 02:15:37,390
Manish escaped overnight.
He has left you alone here.

530
02:15:38,428 --> 02:15:41,295
Now there are only two options
for you.

531
02:15:42,299 --> 02:15:45,427
Do you hear?
Only one place for Janki.

532
02:15:46,303 --> 02:15:48,464
Prison or mental asylum.

533
02:15:49,406 --> 02:15:54,400
''Yes, there can be another option.
lf you agree to me.''

534
02:15:55,479 --> 02:15:57,242
Become your mistress?

535
02:16:00,250 --> 02:16:03,242
Other than your wife does
every woman look like a whore?

536
02:16:04,254 --> 02:16:07,815
Pay someone and have her.
Take advantage of another get laid.

537
02:16:09,259 --> 02:16:12,251
What? Woman leaves home to earn
a livelihood.

538
02:16:12,563 --> 02:16:15,964
And every man assumes
she's his property! Why?

539
02:16:16,266 --> 02:16:20,566
Understand the gravity of
the situation. They want you dead!

540
02:16:21,271 --> 02:16:24,263
You have slighted religion!
- l haven't slighted religion.

541
02:16:25,008 --> 02:16:26,532
l just raised a question.

542
02:16:26,677 --> 02:16:28,941
Which has been rising
in woman's mind for centuries.

543
02:16:29,980 --> 02:16:33,006
They want me dead because
they have no answer!

544
02:16:33,750 --> 02:16:39,950
l'd prefer the madhouse to
living with such illiterate heretics!

545
02:16:42,192 --> 02:16:44,285
Janki is a witch!

546
02:16:44,995 --> 02:16:48,226
Here comes the blatant!
- She has slandered the Ramayana!

547
02:16:48,565 --> 02:16:51,557
She is a prostitute!
- Janki is a slut!

548
02:16:53,503 --> 02:16:56,233
The only place for Janki..
- Prison or madhouse!

549
02:16:56,473 --> 02:16:57,565
Calm down...

550
02:17:00,244 --> 02:17:01,905
''Excuse me, calm down.''

551
02:17:02,646 --> 02:17:06,912
''Janki is not in her senses.
See, the ambulance has come.''

552
02:17:07,251 --> 02:17:11,517
She's going to the hospital.
Please give her way. Let her go.

553
02:17:16,526 --> 02:17:20,519
Where are you going?
Have you gone mad? You stay here.

554
02:17:22,332 --> 02:17:25,563
She's experienced everything!
- She even smokes!

555
02:17:26,270 --> 02:17:30,001
''Slut! Go, drown yourself!
- She has maligned herself everywhere!''

556
02:17:30,274 --> 02:17:33,072
She boozes!
- Whose child are you carrying?

557
02:17:33,343 --> 02:17:35,937
Must be Purushottam's!
- Coming with me?

558
02:17:36,280 --> 02:17:38,874
Move on! What are you glaring at?

559
02:17:38,949 --> 02:17:39,938
No!

560
02:17:41,018 --> 02:17:42,849
Don't!
- What are you doing?

561
02:17:44,788 --> 02:17:46,483
She's pregnant!

562
02:18:17,854 --> 02:18:20,049
''Vaidehi, l lost my baby...''

563
02:18:21,058 --> 02:18:24,255
''No, Janki...
- l've lost it!''

564
02:18:38,008 --> 02:18:39,805
Janki had lost her senses.

565
02:18:40,277 --> 02:18:43,940
''lf she were right in the head,
would she do this on stage?''

566
02:18:44,448 --> 02:18:47,281
She had to go to the asylum
and so she's gone.

567
02:18:48,485 --> 02:18:51,283
Scoundrel! You should
be sent to the asylum!

568
02:18:54,024 --> 02:18:56,788
''No, not even there...''

569
02:18:58,295 --> 02:19:00,286
You won't even spare the lunatics.

570
02:19:01,298 --> 02:19:05,792
A bestial monster like yourself
should be bound in a cage at zoo!

571
02:19:07,104 --> 02:19:09,095
Don't you have any shame
talking to elders like this?

572
02:19:09,306 --> 02:19:13,106
When you have no shame marrying a wife
half your age why should l be ashamed?

573
02:19:13,510 --> 02:19:15,535
''Good gracious.
Lata, go upstairs.''

574
02:19:15,879 --> 02:19:17,972
Women of good homes
shouldn't even hear such words.

575
02:19:18,315 --> 02:19:21,113
''And men of good families,
even with a wife at home...''

576
02:19:21,318 --> 02:19:24,446
have the liberty
to ogle at other women!

577
02:19:25,756 --> 02:19:30,125
You men don't trust your own selves.
That is why you keep women in veil!

578
02:19:30,494 --> 02:19:33,986
You hide her in corners!
lmprison her behind bars!

579
02:19:34,331 --> 02:19:38,631
Keep quiet!
- l won't. l know everything!

580
02:19:39,336 --> 02:19:42,430
Those were your hired goons
who hurt Janki!

581
02:19:43,340 --> 02:19:45,331
l'll tell the police!

582
02:19:46,343 --> 02:19:48,277
Where are you going?

583
02:19:49,079 --> 02:19:50,944
l have called up your husband.

584
02:19:51,281 --> 02:19:54,273
He must be on his way with
the reward and the cops.

585
02:19:54,985 --> 02:19:56,953
Let me go!
- Does one let go of a lakh of rupees?

586
02:19:57,287 --> 02:19:59,084
Leave her.
- Who spoke?

587
02:19:59,356 --> 02:20:01,085
l said let her go!

588
02:20:01,291 --> 02:20:03,521
You know nothing...
- l know everything!

589
02:20:05,228 --> 02:20:09,096
Leave her. Or should l fling this?
And blow your skull to pieces?

590
02:20:09,966 --> 02:20:11,627
Move back! Move!!

591
02:20:16,306 --> 02:20:17,637
Come with me.

592
02:20:19,509 --> 02:20:22,967
l forgive you. Do not return.
Assume your husband is dead.

593
02:20:23,313 --> 02:20:26,305
How can l let my Godlike
husband die so easily?

594
02:20:26,917 --> 02:20:29,317
l still have to take my revenge.

595
02:20:30,754 --> 02:20:35,487
l've fasted for you for so many years.
l too should get some reward for it.

596
02:20:37,127 --> 02:20:39,118
l will return.
Come with me.

597
02:20:39,596 --> 02:20:43,430
She will take revenge.
And the other will lock me in a zoo.

598
02:20:48,405 --> 02:20:51,533
What man? Boozed to the gills?
We've been knocking for so long!

599
02:20:51,975 --> 02:20:54,273
''Are you Purushottam?
- Yes, l am.''

600
02:20:54,544 --> 02:20:57,012
l am Raghuveer. Where is my wife?
- With my wife.

601
02:20:57,280 --> 02:20:59,942
And your wife?
- With your wife.

602
02:21:00,283 --> 02:21:04,982
lf l hit you with my broken arm
your head will split wide open!

603
02:21:05,288 --> 02:21:07,153
Speak the truth!
- That is the truth.

604
02:21:07,290 --> 02:21:09,952
My wife ran away with his wife.

605
02:21:10,293 --> 02:21:13,285
Bad times! l've heard of men
eloping with women.

606
02:21:13,430 --> 02:21:16,092
But for the first time
l'm hearing of women running away!

607
02:21:16,299 --> 02:21:18,290
Devastation! lt's true.
The bell proves it.

608
02:21:21,104 --> 02:21:22,093
Coming.

609
02:21:22,572 --> 02:21:24,972
Vaidehi was seen
in the Awadh Express.

610
02:21:25,442 --> 02:21:26,636
Listen...
- Yes?

611
02:21:26,977 --> 02:21:28,842
lf you find my wife...
- We'll send her.

612
02:21:29,079 --> 02:21:32,879
No! Take her along.
- For what? Rent her out?

613
02:21:33,216 --> 02:21:34,615
Stupid jerk!

614
02:21:58,275 --> 02:22:04,271
''The impish breeze was
flowing in its' own way''

615
02:22:06,283 --> 02:22:10,049
''Somebody gave it agony''

616
02:22:10,420 --> 02:22:12,411
''And took the wings away''

617
02:22:14,858 --> 02:22:20,296
''The impish breeze was
flowing in its' own way''

618
02:22:22,699 --> 02:22:26,294
''Somebody gave it agony''

619
02:22:27,037 --> 02:22:28,971
''And took the wings away''

620
02:22:31,308 --> 02:22:34,641
''The weather changed.
The song broke''

621
02:22:35,011 --> 02:22:38,310
''Silence permeated''

622
02:22:39,115 --> 02:22:42,983
''What path, which city...''

623
02:22:43,320 --> 02:22:46,312
''where are you headed?''

624
02:22:47,257 --> 02:22:54,060
''Tired eyes look for its' home''

625
02:23:30,567 --> 02:23:31,966
Hail Mother!

626
02:23:32,302 --> 02:23:35,100
You? Here? Don't interfere.

627
02:23:35,472 --> 02:23:38,305
l warn you or you
won't leave unscathed!

628
02:23:40,977 --> 02:23:44,310
''Mother, don't worry.
Bulwa is here. He will save us.''

629
02:23:44,714 --> 02:23:46,306
Hear that?

630
02:23:46,449 --> 02:23:50,249
The kid understood.
But you didn't.

631
02:23:52,956 --> 02:23:57,120
Return everyone's stuff.
And quietly jump out the back door.

632
02:23:59,296 --> 02:24:03,062
Don't act too smart!
This isn't your territory!

633
02:24:03,366 --> 02:24:08,770
Dogs have their territories.
Storms and typhoons have no area!

634
02:24:09,406 --> 02:24:13,843
Quickly take your pick.
Do you want to escape or die?

635
02:24:14,177 --> 02:24:18,079
l warn you once again.
- Why are you wasting time arguing?

636
02:24:18,281 --> 02:24:22,081
''lf we chop off his head,
we'll get Rs.200000 as reward!''

637
02:24:22,419 --> 02:24:25,388
Manliness isn't measured
by the length of your moustache.

638
02:24:27,290 --> 02:24:31,818
Those who are men
never hurt women and kids.

639
02:24:32,295 --> 02:24:37,289
''And those who do,
Bulwa loves to hunt such beasts.''

640
02:24:38,368 --> 02:24:40,097
Shut your eyes.

641
02:25:12,502 --> 02:25:14,595
''You, here? Who is this?''

642
02:25:14,938 --> 02:25:17,270
She fainted in the train.
She's also running fever.

643
02:25:17,974 --> 02:25:20,408
Take her to Aunt Dulaari.
- Yes.

644
02:25:22,011 --> 02:25:23,000
Gently...

645
02:25:26,282 --> 02:25:28,011
Keep this.
- No...

646
02:25:28,284 --> 02:25:29,273
Keep it.

647
02:25:29,419 --> 02:25:32,684
Shall l come along?
- No. l'll take her.

648
02:25:33,022 --> 02:25:36,958
''Along with the cops, Gajendra
is looking for you.''

649
02:25:38,428 --> 02:25:43,957
l met Gajendra's dogs in the train.
l cut the tickets for 5 of them.

650
02:25:52,475 --> 02:25:54,238
Feeling very sleepy?

651
02:25:55,245 --> 02:25:56,576
Press properly.

652
02:25:56,846 --> 02:26:00,304
Think of it as my neck
not my leg and press.

653
02:26:00,917 --> 02:26:04,409
''Then your arms will find the strength.
- Master, that's enterprising.''

654
02:26:04,754 --> 02:26:10,249
Only you take advantage of hatred.
You are indeed admirable.

655
02:26:15,131 --> 02:26:17,565
Yes master?
- Has the train arrived?

656
02:26:17,867 --> 02:26:20,267
''Yes, master.
- Whom are you taking?''

657
02:26:21,271 --> 02:26:23,603
A female patient.
- l see.

658
02:26:23,940 --> 02:26:26,272
''Taking her to Dulaari?
- Yes, master.''

659
02:26:26,743 --> 02:26:28,472
Carry on.
- Good day.

660
02:26:36,286 --> 02:26:41,019
She treats everyone.
But she won't treat me.

661
02:26:42,058 --> 02:26:43,787
Congratulations.

662
02:26:45,895 --> 02:26:47,692
The mother and child are fit and fine.

663
02:26:48,031 --> 02:26:51,899
Congratulations.
- ls it a son?

664
02:26:52,368 --> 02:26:56,031
Why do you harp on about
a boy? lt's a goddess.

665
02:26:56,339 --> 02:27:00,241
Girl again!
- Why are you holding your head?

666
02:27:00,643 --> 02:27:02,907
As if it's a problem not a girl.

667
02:27:03,246 --> 02:27:05,646
Have you forgotten
when you were unemployed?

668
02:27:05,982 --> 02:27:10,442
Only after Dhaniya's birth
was your house built.

669
02:27:10,987 --> 02:27:13,478
Damn fool! You've made
so much progress since!

670
02:27:14,057 --> 02:27:17,254
Thank God and sing His praise.

671
02:27:31,274 --> 02:27:34,266
Keep lying. Consider this your house.

672
02:27:35,411 --> 02:27:39,279
''Tell me, where are you going?''

673
02:27:40,283 --> 02:27:45,084
And all alone?
Neither husband nor parents.

674
02:27:48,224 --> 02:27:51,216
All right. Don't talk
if you don't want to.

675
02:27:51,928 --> 02:27:56,661
But don't worry.
Worry harms the baby.

676
02:27:58,234 --> 02:28:02,898
How do you know?
- Listen to her! l'm the midwife here.

677
02:28:04,974 --> 02:28:07,408
Aunt! Hurry!!
- What happened?

678
02:28:07,744 --> 02:28:10,042
Papa and Uncle are drowning
Pooja in milk!

679
02:28:10,313 --> 02:28:11,439
Good God!!

680
02:28:12,248 --> 02:28:14,239
They are out of their minds!

681
02:28:14,584 --> 02:28:17,576
What's the matter?
- The baby that was just born..

682
02:28:17,921 --> 02:28:20,651
Her father wants to kill her
by drowning her in milk!

683
02:28:21,257 --> 02:28:24,749
Dear God! Send her back as a boy!

684
02:28:25,828 --> 02:28:27,523
Accept her back!

685
02:28:28,264 --> 02:28:30,255
''Take her back, dear God!!''

686
02:28:33,002 --> 02:28:33,991
No!

687
02:28:36,839 --> 02:28:40,605
You sinner! What were you up to?

688
02:28:42,278 --> 02:28:47,978
What has this little thing done
to you? She is a gift of God!

689
02:28:48,284 --> 02:28:51,378
But she won't carry brother's name!
The first born is already a girl!

690
02:28:52,689 --> 02:28:54,486
Shut up! Dowry mongers!

691
02:28:55,091 --> 02:28:57,082
You men are a burden to earth!

692
02:28:58,027 --> 02:29:02,361
''lf this was done to your mother,
how would you take birth?''

693
02:29:05,301 --> 02:29:07,030
Murderers! This is a latent mother!

694
02:29:07,637 --> 02:29:11,232
What will remain in the
world if you kill a mother?

695
02:29:12,308 --> 02:29:13,969
My baby...!

696
02:29:21,317 --> 02:29:23,979
You remember 6 dead bodies!
And you're filing the report.

697
02:29:24,120 --> 02:29:27,988
But one living girl is missing
and you know nothing about it!

698
02:29:29,325 --> 02:29:30,986
''Just a minute, Mr. Raghunath.''

699
02:29:31,127 --> 02:29:34,324
They are scared out of their wits
because of the bloodshed.

700
02:29:35,031 --> 02:29:38,990
''But their talk proves this without
doubt, your wife is in this area.''

701
02:29:39,335 --> 02:29:40,927
We will find her.

702
02:29:42,338 --> 02:29:43,669
You will.

703
02:29:44,841 --> 02:29:46,001
You will.

704
02:29:51,280 --> 02:29:53,271
''What is the reward sum?
- 100,000.''

705
02:29:53,383 --> 02:29:56,284
''lncrease it.
Hike it by 200,000 or 5000000''

706
02:29:57,053 --> 02:30:02,685
So much so that whoever has given her
refuge feels greed instead of mercy.

707
02:30:05,094 --> 02:30:08,291
What's the matter?
Why are your hands trembling?

708
02:30:11,034 --> 02:30:16,438
''lf you hadn't reached there in time
they would've killed the child, no?''

709
02:30:18,007 --> 02:30:20,305
They are butchers.

710
02:30:21,110 --> 02:30:22,873
A girl is a burden for them.

711
02:30:24,480 --> 02:30:26,038
Look over there.

712
02:30:26,315 --> 02:30:30,649
That 10 year old girl
is carrying double her weight.

713
02:30:31,521 --> 02:30:35,321
''Now tell me, who is the
burden and who is carrying it!''

714
02:30:37,126 --> 02:30:39,458
And look at 7 year old Kajri.

715
02:30:40,730 --> 02:30:43,528
She stands holding her
little brother on her waist.

716
02:30:44,467 --> 02:30:47,402
lsn't this her age to be playing?

717
02:30:47,737 --> 02:30:51,434
But how will she play? She's
half a mother at this tender age!

718
02:30:51,774 --> 02:30:55,471
When did her childhood
come and leave..? Nobody knows.

719
02:30:57,280 --> 02:31:00,010
ln 2 years she'll be
cooking for her father.

720
02:31:00,283 --> 02:31:06,085
Another 2 years and she'll cook
for her husband and family.

721
02:31:06,422 --> 02:31:08,481
As well as work in the fields.

722
02:31:09,292 --> 02:31:12,955
''ln a short time, she'll bear
a couple of kids and grow old.''

723
02:31:14,430 --> 02:31:19,595
That's a woman's life in our country.
Serve man and die!

724
02:31:20,303 --> 02:31:25,605
And men have the gall to say
that a woman is the door to Hell!

725
02:31:26,309 --> 02:31:30,302
You stupid men have come
to earth via that very door!

726
02:31:31,481 --> 02:31:33,506
Yet they refer to her as a burden!

727
02:31:34,117 --> 02:31:38,520
''Not a burden, woman is the
force that carries burdens!''

728
02:31:39,122 --> 02:31:41,317
Take my own daughter-in-law's example.

729
02:31:42,091 --> 02:31:47,529
''Yes, she is my daughter-in-law.
And my son, her husband...''

730
02:31:47,864 --> 02:31:53,063
''he left his mother, child and wife
and ran away. ln search of God.''

731
02:31:53,402 --> 02:31:56,929
Excrete of a cat!
Of no use to anyone!

732
02:31:57,273 --> 02:32:00,731
''Wretch! Ominous fellow!
- Mother, now stop it.''

733
02:32:01,277 --> 02:32:06,613
Why? Have you ever heard of a
woman running off in search of God?

734
02:32:07,016 --> 02:32:08,950
Deserting her husband and child?

735
02:32:09,452 --> 02:32:13,946
My daughter-in-law performs
the duties my son should have!

736
02:32:14,423 --> 02:32:18,689
''Looked after the house, worked
day and night for her son, Prakash.''

737
02:32:19,028 --> 02:32:21,758
Sent him to school.
- Then to college.

738
02:32:22,031 --> 02:32:25,967
Graduation and now
law studies. L.L.B.

739
02:32:26,102 --> 02:32:28,093
And a computer expert.

740
02:32:28,504 --> 02:32:31,632
He is coming tomorrow
with a computer for me.

741
02:32:32,308 --> 02:32:37,712
Oh yes. lt will be the first computer
in 20 villages! First and only.

742
02:32:38,648 --> 02:32:43,312
''Aunt, you're very fond of English.
- Not fond of..''

743
02:32:43,719 --> 02:32:45,448
l can't help it.

744
02:32:45,621 --> 02:32:48,249
Our own language isn't
appreciated in our nation.

745
02:32:48,391 --> 02:32:50,916
''All around, it's only English.''

746
02:32:51,494 --> 02:32:54,588
So l thought let me learn it.

747
02:32:54,997 --> 02:32:57,056
l memorised huge thick books.

748
02:32:57,400 --> 02:32:59,925
Start to finish.
Just like that only.

749
02:33:12,114 --> 02:33:13,843
Did l say something wrong?

750
02:33:21,090 --> 02:33:23,684
What is the matter?
No work in the fields?

751
02:33:23,993 --> 02:33:29,056
There is but Phoolmati
didn't come to work for 2 days.

752
02:33:29,298 --> 02:33:33,530
''l asked her today and she
says, she won't work anymore.''

753
02:33:35,304 --> 02:33:37,534
Phoolmati has full liberty.

754
02:33:37,974 --> 02:33:43,606
She's the only one in the village
who wears flowers in her hair.

755
02:33:44,313 --> 02:33:49,250
From tomorrow you'll work in my house
not the fields. Serving me. Okay?

756
02:33:49,652 --> 02:33:52,780
''Master, l can't come.''

757
02:33:54,257 --> 02:33:57,658
l... l'm working for Aunt Ram Dulaari.

758
02:33:58,527 --> 02:34:02,588
l'm paid more there.
- Chop it!

759
02:34:02,865 --> 02:34:06,767
Chop her hair off!
And darken her face!

760
02:34:07,270 --> 02:34:13,800
''Lord Ram is the groom.
Music plays all around''

761
02:34:14,176 --> 02:34:16,576
This assignment is ready.

762
02:34:17,280 --> 02:34:21,080
How much for Shahjahanpur?
- l'll tell you tomorrow.

763
02:34:21,517 --> 02:34:24,953
lt is 5 o'clock.
Your shift ends now.

764
02:34:25,288 --> 02:34:28,485
Now go home and cook
dinner for your menfolk.

765
02:34:29,058 --> 02:34:33,290
''And all those who want
advance, take it today.''

766
02:34:33,596 --> 02:34:35,291
l don't want any.

767
02:34:36,365 --> 02:34:38,833
''l want Rs. 100.
- Okay, take it.''

768
02:34:41,304 --> 02:34:43,295
Sign this voucher.

769
02:34:50,246 --> 02:34:54,580
What is this? l've been
teaching you for so long...

770
02:34:54,917 --> 02:34:59,581
and you're still using the thumb?
Sign or l won't give the money!

771
02:34:59,855 --> 02:35:04,315
l can't sign properly as yet.
- No problem. Take your time.

772
02:35:19,275 --> 02:35:20,606
That's better.

773
02:35:25,281 --> 02:35:28,079
''Honestly aunt, you are
doing a darn good job.''

774
02:35:28,417 --> 02:35:33,514
lt's necessary. There's
only one way to reform women.

775
02:35:33,856 --> 02:35:35,517
Education.

776
02:35:36,292 --> 02:35:38,089
And what do they call it...?

777
02:35:43,299 --> 02:35:46,291
You speak quite good English.

778
02:35:52,041 --> 02:35:53,906
What happened to her?

779
02:35:54,243 --> 02:35:58,646
She refused to work in Gajendra's
field. And this is what Birendra did!

780
02:35:58,981 --> 02:36:02,041
What? May vultures feast on
the scoundrel's flesh!

781
02:36:05,054 --> 02:36:07,522
Don't worry.

782
02:36:07,957 --> 02:36:10,391
Wash her face.

783
02:36:11,994 --> 02:36:15,555
Don't you worry. Consider that
you've evaded a problem.

784
02:36:17,266 --> 02:36:21,259
What happened? Who did this?
- Gajendra and Virendra.

785
02:36:22,371 --> 02:36:26,432
These two marauders were
born when 100 demons died!

786
02:36:27,276 --> 02:36:34,079
He was lucky that Bulwa missed.
Or he'd have lost his neck!

787
02:36:35,017 --> 02:36:37,781
He only lost an arm. Nothing else.

788
02:36:38,287 --> 02:36:43,281
The village faced a severe drought
when Bulwa was about 7 years old.

789
02:36:44,026 --> 02:36:48,224
Not a drop of water in the village.
Bulwa's throat was parched.

790
02:36:48,531 --> 02:36:52,228
Gajendra had water in his well.
Bulwa's mother pleaded with him..

791
02:36:53,035 --> 02:36:56,232
The scoundrel put his hand in
her blouse in return for water!

792
02:36:56,906 --> 02:36:59,898
Then his mother threw
the pitcher at his head.

793
02:37:01,577 --> 02:37:04,239
Gajendra accused her of theft.

794
02:37:04,580 --> 02:37:07,572
And sentenced her hands
to be doused in boiling oil.

795
02:37:13,389 --> 02:37:15,914
''Time has changed, not the situation.''

796
02:37:17,960 --> 02:37:20,861
From Bulwa's mother to Phoolmati..

797
02:37:22,431 --> 02:37:25,264
Woman remains in
exactly the same place.

798
02:37:26,402 --> 02:37:28,393
lt will change.

799
02:37:30,005 --> 02:37:32,940
When woman learns to
appreciate herself.

800
02:37:34,009 --> 02:37:38,412
When she respects herself.
Only then will others honour her.

801
02:37:44,286 --> 02:37:47,016
''Are your results out?
- Yes, second division.''

802
02:37:48,457 --> 02:37:52,894
But we had bribed for first division.
- These professors are cheats.

803
02:37:53,229 --> 02:37:56,892
Tomorrow itself l'll beat them up
The next exam will be in hospital.

804
02:37:58,033 --> 02:38:01,230
Let it be. But do warn them.

805
02:38:01,570 --> 02:38:05,904
Next time if my child doesn't
top. l'll open up his top.

806
02:38:08,010 --> 02:38:10,001
So what's the news about
my darling daughter?

807
02:38:10,246 --> 02:38:11,440
l'm fine.

808
02:38:12,414 --> 02:38:17,784
You've come at the right time.
Write me a speech for the election.

809
02:38:18,254 --> 02:38:20,916
Ask Prakash to write.
He's very smart.

810
02:38:21,257 --> 02:38:24,590
Who is he? Pandey's son?
- No..

811
02:38:24,927 --> 02:38:29,728
''He must be Harpat's son.
- No, Aunt Ram Dulaari's son.''

812
02:38:31,267 --> 02:38:34,964
Ram Dulaari's son?
- Son of a low caste! lmpossible!

813
02:38:35,271 --> 02:38:40,675
He's very capable. He's getting a
computer from the city for his mother.

814
02:38:41,010 --> 02:38:44,275
What's that? Spare part of a tractor?

815
02:38:45,080 --> 02:38:49,949
A computer is a miracle.
lt alone can do the work of 10 men!

816
02:38:50,286 --> 02:38:51,844
Really?
- Yes.

817
02:38:52,087 --> 02:38:54,282
Can it lift my tractor by itself?

818
02:38:56,091 --> 02:39:00,027
Dimwit! This is why
l'd tell you to study.

819
02:39:02,031 --> 02:39:04,022
Take your uncle to see the computer.

820
02:39:04,300 --> 02:39:08,862
Check what Ram Dulaari intends
doing with the computer here.

821
02:39:15,511 --> 02:39:17,308
Bless me.
- God bless.

822
02:39:20,249 --> 02:39:23,309
''Okay, now put this away
and you sit here.''

823
02:39:24,320 --> 02:39:26,481
Now inaugurate it.

824
02:39:27,122 --> 02:39:29,784
''Do you remember how?
- Yes, l know all.''

825
02:39:30,125 --> 02:39:34,323
You taught me. First..
l press this button. Right?

826
02:39:46,008 --> 02:39:47,771
This is a miracle!

827
02:39:51,447 --> 02:39:53,540
See that?
- This really is a miracle!

828
02:39:57,853 --> 02:40:00,413
How is it?
- Beautiful.

829
02:40:01,290 --> 02:40:02,518
Glorious.

830
02:40:03,525 --> 02:40:08,292
l've never seen this lady before.
- We've come to see the computer!

831
02:40:11,300 --> 02:40:12,289
lt's nice.

832
02:40:13,869 --> 02:40:16,099
Nice... let's leave.

833
02:40:16,972 --> 02:40:18,303
What a wonder!

834
02:40:23,045 --> 02:40:24,945
There! Gone again.

835
02:40:25,614 --> 02:40:27,707
The light goes more
often that it remains.

836
02:40:29,018 --> 02:40:33,580
You will laugh. You have electricity.
Only my home is dark.

837
02:40:35,024 --> 02:40:36,013
l'll leave.

838
02:40:36,325 --> 02:40:41,524
You just came. The city was better.
We'd meet more often.

839
02:40:41,864 --> 02:40:43,991
''We'd go out, watch films.''

840
02:40:44,333 --> 02:40:46,995
Here you stay aloof.
You don't meet at all!

841
02:40:47,269 --> 02:40:52,366
Meeting is fine but what next?
lf somebody finds out...

842
02:40:53,275 --> 02:40:55,743
The very thought scares me.
- There you go again!

843
02:40:56,078 --> 02:41:00,071
''l told you, when you stand first in
the state and your photo...''

844
02:41:00,282 --> 02:41:04,776
is published then nobody will object
and l'll convince Papa too.

845
02:41:05,220 --> 02:41:07,450
So this is the plan?

846
02:41:08,424 --> 02:41:10,585
May God fulfill your wish.

847
02:41:11,060 --> 02:41:14,086
Now l better leave or l'll
miss the last bus to Makhanpur.

848
02:41:14,296 --> 02:41:18,096
When will you return?
- Friends' wedding is at night.

849
02:41:18,434 --> 02:41:20,629
l'll return by the morning bus.
- Sure?

850
02:41:20,803 --> 02:41:21,792
Yes.

851
02:41:25,874 --> 02:41:30,368
Special announcement.
A lady named Vaidehi Bajaj..

852
02:41:30,713 --> 02:41:32,010
Brother!
- Yes?

853
02:41:32,314 --> 02:41:36,444
l saw this woman.
- Really? Where?

854
02:41:36,785 --> 02:41:39,310
At Ram Dulaari's.
- Dimwit. You are drunk.

855
02:41:39,621 --> 02:41:43,489
What would a girl from
the city do in the village?

856
02:41:43,826 --> 02:41:48,923
Birendra can't be wrong
where women are concerned.

857
02:41:49,264 --> 02:41:51,630
Just a minute.
- What are you up to?

858
02:41:51,967 --> 02:41:54,401
A reward of Rs. 10 lakhs.
- 0... 9..

859
02:41:59,241 --> 02:42:04,543
''Birendra, younger brother of
Gajendra from Bhawanipur here.''

860
02:42:04,947 --> 02:42:06,676
Yes?
- Your madam...

861
02:42:06,949 --> 02:42:10,282
the photo on television..
Are you listening?

862
02:42:12,287 --> 02:42:16,690
l heard it in the garden! Was he born
with a loudspeaker? What says he?

863
02:42:18,293 --> 02:42:22,627
ls what you're saying right?
- Cent per cent.

864
02:42:22,898 --> 02:42:27,096
Bring the money and take the girl.

865
02:42:28,837 --> 02:42:32,102
Fine. We'll meet at the
address you said tomorrow.

866
02:42:32,474 --> 02:42:36,808
l've arranged for you
to win the election!

867
02:42:37,112 --> 02:42:39,103
We'll kidnap the city girl.

868
02:42:40,315 --> 02:42:42,647
''Master, l've cut the connection.
- Well done.''

869
02:42:42,918 --> 02:42:46,319
What connection?
- Ram Dulaari's electric connection.

870
02:42:46,555 --> 02:42:53,051
She has been teaching computer to
the oafs. Now let's see her teach!

871
02:42:53,962 --> 02:42:58,399
lt's only the electric
connection that's been cut. But..

872
02:42:59,268 --> 02:43:04,604
The connection of this house
is tightly connected to hers.

873
02:43:07,476 --> 02:43:10,934
What do you mean?
- Sushma is slipping.

874
02:43:12,981 --> 02:43:16,508
What the heck are you saying?
l'll chop your tongue to pieces!

875
02:43:16,852 --> 02:43:21,084
My tongue and eyes belong to you.

876
02:43:21,523 --> 02:43:26,790
l did see Sushma with Ram
Dulaari's son Prakash.

877
02:43:36,405 --> 02:43:38,965
Where will that boy be found? Where?

878
02:43:39,308 --> 02:43:41,970
He has gone to Makhanpur.
For a friend's wedding.

879
02:43:42,911 --> 02:43:45,209
He will return by the morning bus.

880
02:43:52,988 --> 02:43:56,719
Brother... don't worry one bit.

881
02:43:59,261 --> 02:44:00,751
Don't worry one bit.

882
02:44:02,264 --> 02:44:05,427
Prakash who dared to
lay his eyes on Sushma...

883
02:44:05,601 --> 02:44:08,001
l'll kill him and
bury him in the field!

884
02:44:08,270 --> 02:44:10,465
No... no little one.

885
02:44:12,274 --> 02:44:16,438
Such an easy death won't
give my heart any solace.

886
02:44:18,280 --> 02:44:20,942
Nor will that lowly
caste learn a lesson.

887
02:44:22,284 --> 02:44:23,273
No.

888
02:44:24,286 --> 02:44:25,878
Castrate the rascal!

889
02:44:27,189 --> 02:44:28,952
Chop and hurl his weapon away!

890
02:44:32,294 --> 02:44:34,421
Seems like a long drawn affair.

891
02:44:36,031 --> 02:44:37,293
Nothing new.

892
02:44:41,470 --> 02:44:42,630
What happened?

893
02:44:44,473 --> 02:44:47,533
Once there was a
wedding in our village.

894
02:44:48,243 --> 02:44:50,575
Suddenly the lights went out.

895
02:44:51,046 --> 02:44:57,042
Do you know whom the groom
garlanded instead of the bride?

896
02:44:57,953 --> 02:44:59,716
His own mother-in-law!

897
02:45:09,264 --> 02:45:11,061
Hang on.

898
02:45:14,536 --> 02:45:17,994
What happened? Why
are you so frightened?

899
02:45:18,273 --> 02:45:23,677
Do something fast! Send message
to Prakash not to return.

900
02:45:24,012 --> 02:45:25,741
Why?
- His life is in danger!

901
02:45:25,948 --> 02:45:31,284
Good God! What are you saying?
Why would his life be in danger?

902
02:45:32,955 --> 02:45:36,948
What has he done? Tell me.
Who wants to kill him?

903
02:45:37,459 --> 02:45:38,619
Tell me!

904
02:45:40,529 --> 02:45:41,791
My Papa.

905
02:45:43,465 --> 02:45:44,489
Why?

906
02:45:46,969 --> 02:45:49,904
Why?
- He has found out..

907
02:45:50,238 --> 02:45:52,900
Prakash and l love each other.

908
02:45:56,244 --> 02:45:57,575
Love?

909
02:45:58,947 --> 02:46:02,041
Wretch! Why did you do this? Why?

910
02:46:02,484 --> 02:46:06,921
Why did you do this? Oh why?

911
02:46:11,393 --> 02:46:13,258
Woe upon us!

912
02:46:14,496 --> 02:46:18,592
Woe upon us!
We will be destroyed!

913
02:46:20,135 --> 02:46:21,932
We are ruined!

914
02:46:22,404 --> 02:46:29,071
''All my efforts, my penance....
she shattered all my dreams!''

915
02:46:32,280 --> 02:46:33,679
We are ruined!

916
02:46:35,450 --> 02:46:39,750
Couldn't she find anybody other
than my son in this world?

917
02:46:41,356 --> 02:46:44,291
We are ruined! Ruined!

918
02:46:48,296 --> 02:46:51,390
''Child, l beg you...''

919
02:46:51,967 --> 02:46:55,528
l beseech you
spare his life!

920
02:46:56,972 --> 02:47:01,568
Don't take him away from me!
l have nobody but him!

921
02:47:04,946 --> 02:47:09,383
Forget him. Please.
- l'll forget everything.

922
02:47:11,253 --> 02:47:13,483
But save his life!

923
02:47:13,989 --> 02:47:17,049
l'll go to Makhanpur if you won't.

924
02:47:17,559 --> 02:47:18,548
No!

925
02:47:19,061 --> 02:47:21,256
No! You don't go there!

926
02:47:22,064 --> 02:47:27,263
l will go but l won't
let you go there. never.

927
02:47:45,387 --> 02:47:47,878
''As soon as dawn breaks,
that boy will be...''

928
02:47:53,228 --> 02:47:54,752
''My respects, master.''

929
02:47:57,766 --> 02:48:02,362
The child had a tummy ache.
l've given her the medicine.

930
02:48:04,473 --> 02:48:08,375
lt was quite late in
the night so l thought..

931
02:48:09,244 --> 02:48:11,371
l'll escort the child home.

932
02:48:11,680 --> 02:48:13,238
Go to your room.

933
02:48:21,990 --> 02:48:25,983
''l'll take leave, master.
- Won't you take your fees?''

934
02:48:28,997 --> 02:48:31,591
''No master, there's no need.''

935
02:48:31,933 --> 02:48:35,596
''Are you doing me a favour?
- No, master. That's not true.''

936
02:48:35,937 --> 02:48:40,033
Take it if brother
gives it with love.

937
02:48:40,075 --> 02:48:41,542
Come...come here.

938
02:49:06,301 --> 02:49:08,292
You're no human but a beast!

939
02:49:12,307 --> 02:49:14,104
Shut up.
- No yelling.

940
02:49:14,709 --> 02:49:17,439
We'll parade both of you
naked through the village!

941
02:49:17,779 --> 02:49:20,475
She's the woman l told you about!

942
02:49:22,317 --> 02:49:27,050
Lock Ram Dulaari in her own house.
And lock this woman upstairs.

943
02:49:27,389 --> 02:49:31,792
''No, master! Let her go!
She has nothing to do with this.''

944
02:49:32,127 --> 02:49:35,324
She's in grave trouble!
- We'll erase her troubles.

945
02:49:35,497 --> 02:49:38,466
Her husband is coming
with 10 lakhs tomorrow.

946
02:49:39,634 --> 02:49:42,228
''Master, no..!
- Take her away!''

947
02:49:42,504 --> 02:49:44,335
''Let her go, master.''

948
02:49:44,906 --> 02:49:46,601
Take her away!
- Master!!

949
02:49:51,747 --> 02:49:55,148
Listen...!
Sushma isn't in her room.

950
02:49:55,484 --> 02:49:57,213
The city woman too is missing.

951
02:50:02,858 --> 02:50:06,157
The city lady has kidnapped Sushma!

952
02:50:06,495 --> 02:50:08,963
l'm sure they've gone
to the bus station!

953
02:50:14,569 --> 02:50:16,434
Stop! Stop the bus!

954
02:50:18,907 --> 02:50:21,102
What's the matter?
- You can't go to the village!

955
02:50:21,310 --> 02:50:24,370
We must go back to the city.
- Why to the city?

956
02:50:24,713 --> 02:50:27,705
No questions. We must leave. Pronto!
- What's wrong?

957
02:50:27,849 --> 02:50:30,010
''ls everything all right back home?
- Yes, come on!''

958
02:51:03,418 --> 02:51:04,749
Praise the Mother!

959
02:51:08,056 --> 02:51:12,755
Our enmity is different
from this matter here.

960
02:51:12,894 --> 02:51:16,261
Ram Dulaari's son has
kidnapped Sushma!

961
02:51:17,432 --> 02:51:19,696
And this city lass supported him!

962
02:51:20,702 --> 02:51:22,499
''No, l came of my own accord!''

963
02:51:22,704 --> 02:51:25,502
''Whatever it be, now it's a
matter of Gajendra's honour!''

964
02:51:25,807 --> 02:51:27,798
Hats off to your Gajendra!

965
02:51:28,443 --> 02:51:31,173
He has no concern for
the honour of the poor.

966
02:51:31,513 --> 02:51:34,505
''Whenever he feels like it,
rubs and snuffs it!''

967
02:51:34,716 --> 02:51:37,514
''When it comes to himself,
he screams in anguish!''

968
02:51:37,853 --> 02:51:41,380
When he has sown bitterness
how can he reap sweetness?

969
02:51:41,523 --> 02:51:47,393
Once again we warn you hand them over
to us! Gajendra will settle scores.

970
02:51:47,729 --> 02:51:51,529
Will he do justice? The one
who starves his employees...

971
02:51:51,733 --> 02:51:54,725
to fill his godowns?
Will he do justice?

972
02:51:56,071 --> 02:52:00,804
The one who sheds the blood of
innocents in the name of caste?

973
02:52:01,877 --> 02:52:06,541
Tries to dishonour a poor woman
asking for water in times of drought.

974
02:52:06,748 --> 02:52:10,741
Will that Gajendra do justice?
l will do justice now!

975
02:52:11,420 --> 02:52:15,550
This boy kidnapped the girl.
l will bring the father here!

976
02:52:15,891 --> 02:52:20,351
l'll rip his skin and make a poor
man wear the shoe made from it!

977
02:52:21,496 --> 02:52:23,487
What are you waiting for?
He's alone. Kill him!

978
02:52:23,698 --> 02:52:24,687
Bravo!

979
02:53:30,499 --> 02:53:34,367
''Fine, now suffer the consequences
of Gajendra's fury! Now he will..''

980
02:53:34,703 --> 02:53:35,692
Quiet!

981
02:53:36,037 --> 02:53:39,495
He wets his pants when l roar here!

982
02:53:39,908 --> 02:53:41,102
His fury?

983
02:53:41,510 --> 02:53:44,035
He won't go to shit
without four gun-toting men!

984
02:53:44,446 --> 02:53:46,243
Threatening me with him!

985
02:53:58,727 --> 02:54:05,223
''Prakash, Sushma and the girl
have gone to the woods. To Bulwa.''

986
02:54:15,010 --> 02:54:19,674
This morning my niece eloped
with a boy from a low caste.

987
02:54:20,682 --> 02:54:22,479
Vaidehi too left with them.

988
02:54:22,951 --> 02:54:25,010
''Yes, terribly dammit!''

989
02:54:25,554 --> 02:54:27,681
The entire house is
dammit with sorrow.

990
02:54:28,690 --> 02:54:31,853
Yours is a professional runner.
Ours eloped for the first time.

991
02:54:32,427 --> 02:54:35,487
See my elder brother
He's furious with anger.

992
02:54:37,299 --> 02:54:40,359
''Any other time, we'd
have burnt down the village!''

993
02:54:40,702 --> 02:54:42,693
But what can we do?
lt's election time.

994
02:54:43,038 --> 02:54:45,506
With great difficulty
brother got the ticket.

995
02:54:45,941 --> 02:54:48,842
''Have you found out where she is?
- She's with our enemy, Bulwa.''

996
02:54:49,711 --> 02:54:53,704
He's a very dangerous man.
- Where will l find this danger?

997
02:54:54,015 --> 02:54:58,952
Where and how and when and if
at all he'll be... He decides that.

998
02:55:09,531 --> 02:55:11,055
Praise the Mother.

999
02:55:12,467 --> 02:55:16,301
''Are you Bulwa?
- Yes, l am.''

1000
02:55:17,405 --> 02:55:20,169
Where is Vaidehi?
Call her. l want to see her.

1001
02:55:20,675 --> 02:55:22,404
l'll have to ask her.

1002
02:55:22,677 --> 02:55:26,169
She's my wife!
- This too l must confirm.

1003
02:55:33,989 --> 02:55:38,358
Can't blame you for this.
Times are bad.

1004
02:55:39,494 --> 02:55:45,194
But not here. We are much
behind time and low in society.

1005
02:55:45,700 --> 02:55:48,032
But a little higher in principles.

1006
02:55:48,703 --> 02:55:52,366
Honesty in my pockets and l risk
my life... that's my asset.

1007
02:55:53,041 --> 02:55:56,704
Every woman is my mother
and l don't sell my mother!

1008
02:55:57,045 --> 02:55:58,569
Blessed is the Mother.

1009
02:56:00,415 --> 02:56:02,383
You talk of high ideals.

1010
02:56:02,717 --> 02:56:05,447
Whereas you keep another
man's wife by force...

1011
02:56:05,520 --> 02:56:10,287
Mind your tongue!
Else l'll chop it off right here!

1012
02:56:10,525 --> 02:56:12,584
And you won't be able
to convey a word to Gajendra!

1013
02:56:13,428 --> 02:56:15,225
Look..
- Meeting adjourned.

1014
02:56:17,165 --> 02:56:20,862
l'll get her to Malai Ghat tomorrow
morning. Come and meet her.

1015
02:56:21,670 --> 02:56:25,470
But no use of force.
And come all alone.

1016
02:56:26,374 --> 02:56:28,842
The sentence for
being untrue is death!

1017
02:56:29,477 --> 02:56:31,138
Blessed is the Mother.

1018
02:56:44,392 --> 02:56:47,850
What's the matter?
Why are you crying?

1019
02:56:48,963 --> 02:56:51,488
Because at this moment our daughter..

1020
02:56:51,866 --> 02:56:55,859
is ravaging her honour
lying with that low caste boy.

1021
02:56:56,971 --> 02:57:00,031
And her crazy father
is cremating her.

1022
02:57:02,711 --> 02:57:06,112
She died the day she
shamed us by leaving!

1023
02:57:07,849 --> 02:57:09,214
Offer flowers!

1024
02:57:09,718 --> 02:57:11,049
She is dead!

1025
02:57:12,721 --> 02:57:13,710
Go on!

1026
02:57:17,592 --> 02:57:20,823
Send all our men with
this man to Malai Ghat.

1027
02:57:21,429 --> 02:57:24,796
Bulwa and all his men should be
hacked and thrown in the river!

1028
02:57:27,869 --> 02:57:29,666
We're helping each other because..

1029
02:57:29,804 --> 02:57:33,672
you want Bulwa dead
and l want my wife. Safe

1030
02:57:33,808 --> 02:57:37,437
Two minutes. Two minutes
is all you have.

1031
02:57:37,812 --> 02:57:41,339
Either by force or
anyhow save your wife.

1032
02:57:41,683 --> 02:57:43,674
l'm not responsible for anything.

1033
02:58:13,715 --> 02:58:17,116
Do not be afraid.
Go ahead and meet him.

1034
02:58:33,735 --> 02:58:37,728
''Go on. Sit in the launch.
- Now look, Raghu. Don't use force...''

1035
02:58:38,540 --> 02:58:39,734
We have no time.

1036
02:58:40,742 --> 02:58:44,371
That man you're banking on
is going to be dead in 2 minutes.

1037
02:58:47,248 --> 02:58:49,148
Bulwa! Run away!

1038
02:59:00,762 --> 02:59:04,163
Glory to the Goddess!

1039
03:00:19,040 --> 03:00:22,100
Betrayal will be punished
with death. l told you.

1040
03:00:23,378 --> 03:00:25,710
But you couldn't get it
in your skull...

1041
03:00:33,721 --> 03:00:35,951
You women are your
own worst enemies!

1042
03:00:36,524 --> 03:00:37,718
Go to hell!

1043
03:00:38,726 --> 03:00:42,526
You ought to be thankful you
haven't married an alien...

1044
03:00:42,864 --> 03:00:45,389
you have married a girl
from your own country.

1045
03:00:45,733 --> 03:00:49,726
''Only she could be horrified at your
death, despite all your atrocities.''

1046
03:00:50,271 --> 03:00:54,367
''Or else, your head would have
rolled off your shoulders!''

1047
03:01:03,751 --> 03:01:07,949
''lt isn't just about the baby, Raghu.
lt's about my self-respect.''

1048
03:01:09,757 --> 03:01:11,748
And that's what l'm
trying to protect.

1049
03:01:44,192 --> 03:01:46,057
What a slur on our name!

1050
03:01:49,464 --> 03:01:52,126
lf we don't do something
about it even now...

1051
03:01:52,233 --> 03:01:55,896
the community is going to
call us a bunch of eunuchs.

1052
03:01:57,739 --> 03:02:01,140
What are we to do?
What...?

1053
03:02:01,342 --> 03:02:03,242
We must humiliate Bulwa...

1054
03:02:03,544 --> 03:02:06,138
and teach the lower-castes
a lesson!

1055
03:02:08,983 --> 03:02:12,749
Ram Dulaari!

1056
03:02:13,254 --> 03:02:14,243
No!

1057
03:02:23,231 --> 03:02:24,698
No!

1058
03:02:24,766 --> 03:02:27,826
Give that to me... Give it!
- No!

1059
03:02:33,508 --> 03:02:35,703
Don't anyone dare come closer!

1060
03:02:41,015 --> 03:02:45,042
''Mother! Save me, Mother!''

1061
03:02:50,725 --> 03:02:55,719
''Samariya! Aunt Laxmi...
save me, someone!''

1062
03:02:57,732 --> 03:02:59,723
l have done no harm to anybody!

1063
03:03:00,735 --> 03:03:05,229
Spare me...!
Please let me go!

1064
03:03:05,807 --> 03:03:07,399
Mother!

1065
03:03:11,546 --> 03:03:13,980
Let me go! Please leave me alone!

1066
03:03:14,549 --> 03:03:15,538
Don't!

1067
03:03:20,888 --> 03:03:25,086
Nathu...? You?
You've been a brother to me!

1068
03:03:26,494 --> 03:03:29,691
''Let me go, my son...
Please leave me alone!''

1069
03:03:30,431 --> 03:03:33,093
God! What am l to do...?
Where am l to go?

1070
03:03:35,703 --> 03:03:38,900
''Mangal!
What are you doing, my son?''

1071
03:03:39,440 --> 03:03:41,499
l've always been an aunt to you!

1072
03:03:41,876 --> 03:03:45,710
''Spare me...
Please let me go, my son!''

1073
03:03:46,714 --> 03:03:48,648
Let me go... Nandu!

1074
03:03:50,718 --> 03:03:53,915
''Mother! Birju...
come to my rescue, someone!''

1075
03:04:03,931 --> 03:04:05,398
Hold her down!

1076
03:04:55,983 --> 03:04:57,883
''Last night, Gajendra and Virendra...''

1077
03:04:58,719 --> 03:05:03,713
raped Ram Dulaari
and burnt her alive!

1078
03:06:15,930 --> 03:06:20,333
Master! We have captured Bulwa!
We bring him here in chains!

1079
03:06:34,682 --> 03:06:35,671
Bravo!

1080
03:06:36,684 --> 03:06:40,017
''With the lion bound in chains,
Gajendra comes out in the open!''

1081
03:06:40,421 --> 03:06:42,446
lt's exactly after 14 years...

1082
03:06:43,424 --> 03:06:44,413
6 months...

1083
03:06:44,692 --> 03:06:45,818
8 days...

1084
03:06:46,694 --> 03:06:50,892
''and 4 hours, that l get
to see you again.''

1085
03:06:51,933 --> 03:06:53,764
l remember everything.

1086
03:06:57,705 --> 03:07:00,697
You were bound to remember
every moment!

1087
03:07:01,275 --> 03:07:04,369
l left you with a single hand...
to wash and feed yourself!

1088
03:07:06,113 --> 03:07:09,708
Throw him at my feet!
l'm going to carve him to pieces!

1089
03:07:10,017 --> 03:07:13,714
They aren't your men.
They're my men.

1090
03:07:15,523 --> 03:07:18,515
''To ferret a snake like you out of
its pit, this was the only way!''

1091
03:07:19,660 --> 03:07:24,063
''With a dagger held to his back,
man will do anything he's asked to!''

1092
03:08:41,742 --> 03:08:43,073
Bravo!

1093
03:08:43,844 --> 03:08:46,074
l looked for you among the men...

1094
03:08:47,548 --> 03:08:49,413
''and here you were,
hiding behind the women''

1095
03:08:49,750 --> 03:08:50,910
Bloody eunuch!

1096
03:08:51,252 --> 03:08:56,918
Had you attacked me in a sari...
l might yet have spared you.

1097
03:09:08,536 --> 03:09:10,265
Bulwa! Where are you going?

1098
03:09:10,771 --> 03:09:12,898
''Bulwa! Kill me, before you leave!''

1099
03:09:13,441 --> 03:09:16,433
Know what? l was the one
who raped Ramdulaari!

1100
03:09:16,777 --> 03:09:19,507
''For your mother's sake, Bulwa...
Kill me, before you go!''

1101
03:09:22,850 --> 03:09:27,048
Bulwa! The para-military forces
are here. Gajendra has fled.

1102
03:09:27,221 --> 03:09:28,711
Let's escape! C'mon!

1103
03:09:55,749 --> 03:09:57,740
Hurry up! Quick!

1104
03:10:09,763 --> 03:10:13,426
Behind the hillock is an
army camp. Go ahead safely.

1105
03:10:13,767 --> 03:10:17,100
There's no danger there. Go on!
- How about you?

1106
03:10:17,571 --> 03:10:20,404
You're badly hurt! You must go
to a hospital. Come with us.

1107
03:10:20,708 --> 03:10:23,939
l'm okay. But your life
is in danger. Go on!

1108
03:10:24,445 --> 03:10:28,438
Who do you think you are? What will
you achieve in this condition?

1109
03:10:28,716 --> 03:10:32,049
''All your men are dead!
And you will die, too!''

1110
03:10:39,727 --> 03:10:41,388
l'm the jinxed one

1111
03:10:43,497 --> 03:10:46,125
l bring misfortune to everyone.

1112
03:10:47,601 --> 03:10:50,399
''Maithili, Janki,
Ramdulaari...''

1113
03:10:52,740 --> 03:10:54,401
''and now, it's you.''

1114
03:10:55,476 --> 03:11:00,243
Do not hold yourself responsible.
And do not grieve for them.

1115
03:11:01,415 --> 03:11:05,408
They were brave women
who fought the hypocrites.

1116
03:11:05,953 --> 03:11:08,547
They took on a system
fraught with evil customs.

1117
03:11:08,889 --> 03:11:12,154
And suffering is a
part of one's struggle.

1118
03:11:12,493 --> 03:11:16,520
Have faith in them. Their sacrifice
will not go in vain.

1119
03:11:19,433 --> 03:11:21,196
And do not worry about me.

1120
03:11:21,902 --> 03:11:25,895
Death cannot claim me.
Bulwa is immortal.

1121
03:11:26,473 --> 03:11:30,204
Whenever someone raises a cry
against atrocities and injustice...

1122
03:11:30,511 --> 03:11:32,445
''be sure, Bulwa is somewhere around.''

1123
03:11:34,715 --> 03:11:36,376
l know only this much...

1124
03:11:37,518 --> 03:11:41,386
Humans are those who raise their
voice against injustice.

1125
03:11:41,722 --> 03:11:43,383
They're among the living.

1126
03:11:49,897 --> 03:11:51,728
Glory to the Goddess.

1127
03:11:56,070 --> 03:11:57,401
Glory to the Goddess.

1128
03:12:13,754 --> 03:12:17,918
No praise is enough
for Gajendra Babu.

1129
03:12:18,259 --> 03:12:22,025
''Despite the tragedy back home,
he's here to take part...''

1130
03:12:22,196 --> 03:12:24,687
in the annual day celebrations
of our organization.

1131
03:12:25,165 --> 03:12:26,689
That speaks for his greatness.

1132
03:12:26,834 --> 03:12:31,498
l now request the retired
Chief Justice Mr Srivastava...

1133
03:12:31,839 --> 03:12:35,206
to come to the stage and
felicitate Gajendra Babu.

1134
03:12:47,721 --> 03:12:48,710
Thank you.

1135
03:12:57,731 --> 03:12:59,926
A man who rapes women...

1136
03:13:00,734 --> 03:13:03,259
has no right to beget such honour.

1137
03:13:03,737 --> 03:13:06,900
Go away. You don't know who l am.

1138
03:13:07,241 --> 03:13:12,178
l know. A man who can
rape a pregnant woman...

1139
03:13:12,413 --> 03:13:14,404
can rape his own mother too.

1140
03:13:15,749 --> 03:13:19,344
And you know what you call
such people in your own words.

1141
03:13:25,893 --> 03:13:26,917
Who are you?

1142
03:13:30,698 --> 03:13:34,429
This... this is the
real Gajendra Singh!

1143
03:13:35,703 --> 03:13:38,433
l wanted to expose him
to all of you.

1144
03:13:38,706 --> 03:13:41,436
He's the man who raped Ramdulaari.

1145
03:13:43,177 --> 03:13:44,872
He burnt her alive!

1146
03:13:45,479 --> 03:13:47,709
And you folks are felicitating him...
- She's lying!

1147
03:13:49,049 --> 03:13:51,882
She's a whore!
A woman having loose-moral.

1148
03:13:52,720 --> 03:13:55,518
''She's pregnant, but she's
running away from her husband.''

1149
03:13:56,090 --> 03:13:58,081
She has illicit relations
with the bandit Bulwa!

1150
03:13:59,026 --> 03:14:03,224
''He has instigated her and sent her
here, to level accusations at me!''

1151
03:14:03,731 --> 03:14:05,562
What are you watching?
Throw her out.

1152
03:14:05,666 --> 03:14:06,598
Get out...
- Hold it.

1153
03:14:07,201 --> 03:14:08,463
What do you wish to say?

1154
03:14:08,736 --> 03:14:11,398
You're a woman! And you lie in
the presence of so many men.

1155
03:14:11,739 --> 03:14:13,934
Don't you feel any shame?
- l do!

1156
03:14:17,878 --> 03:14:21,678
l do feel a sense of shame!

1157
03:14:22,916 --> 03:14:29,685
A land where womenfolk are given
the exalted position of Goddesses...

1158
03:14:31,825 --> 03:14:36,353
a land where people
scale mountains...

1159
03:14:36,697 --> 03:14:38,824
singing glories to
the Goddess Mother...

1160
03:14:40,701 --> 03:14:44,762
''a woman, a mother, was
raped and burnt alive.''

1161
03:14:46,407 --> 03:14:48,705
And no one even bothered to enquire.

1162
03:14:51,044 --> 03:14:54,036
Such is the hypocrisy of a nation
in which l was born.

1163
03:14:55,716 --> 03:14:57,911
l'm ashamed of that.

1164
03:14:59,720 --> 03:15:02,382
To see my menfolk remain mute
spectators to atrocities...

1165
03:15:02,723 --> 03:15:04,714
''perpetrated in their presence,...''

1166
03:15:05,726 --> 03:15:09,423
l feel ashamed to acknowledge
their impotency.

1167
03:15:11,732 --> 03:15:15,896
l feel ashamed when l see
womenfolk rendered helpless.

1168
03:15:18,539 --> 03:15:22,669
''This is what women should do.
And this, they mustn't.''

1169
03:15:24,411 --> 03:15:27,676
''This is right for her,
and this is wrong.''

1170
03:15:29,550 --> 03:15:33,350
''To those who shackle the minds
of the womenfolk, l ask...''

1171
03:15:34,688 --> 03:15:39,182
how many more sacrifices do you need?
How many of us will you kill?

1172
03:15:41,695 --> 03:15:44,926
''Even today, in several villages...''

1173
03:15:46,900 --> 03:15:50,495
the female child is killed at birth.

1174
03:15:53,507 --> 03:15:56,374
''Several unmarried girls
kill themselves,...''

1175
03:15:56,710 --> 03:15:59,873
for fear of not taking enough dowry
to their in-laws.

1176
03:16:01,215 --> 03:16:03,945
And yet others are burnt alive
after marriage.

1177
03:16:05,719 --> 03:16:08,517
Even before a girl
can think for herself...

1178
03:16:08,922 --> 03:16:10,787
she is married away...

1179
03:16:11,859 --> 03:16:16,296
as if she were a burden
they want to get rid of.

1180
03:16:17,965 --> 03:16:20,798
A woman who has not borne a child...

1181
03:16:22,402 --> 03:16:25,064
is spurned with the label
of a barren woman.

1182
03:16:26,273 --> 03:16:30,175
ls a woman only a
baby-producing machine then?

1183
03:16:31,845 --> 03:16:34,473
Does she have no personality
of her own?

1184
03:16:35,682 --> 03:16:37,673
Does she have no identity
she can call her own?

1185
03:16:40,687 --> 03:16:45,090
There are people who raise a storm
in the name of culture and religion.

1186
03:16:46,293 --> 03:16:49,228
Why don't they raise a voice
against these evils?

1187
03:16:51,398 --> 03:16:56,028
l have no witnesses
against this man.

1188
03:16:56,703 --> 03:16:57,863
None

1189
03:16:58,705 --> 03:17:03,165
''ln a society where the one who
speaks the truth is declared ''mad''...''

1190
03:17:03,510 --> 03:17:05,842
''and the one who remains silent
is called ''wise''...''

1191
03:17:06,713 --> 03:17:08,442
who will ever speak the truth?

1192
03:17:10,517 --> 03:17:16,012
''l have spoken the truth. And l know,
l will be burnt alive today.''

1193
03:17:16,723 --> 03:17:20,989
And why not?
Because this is the nation...

1194
03:17:22,329 --> 03:17:25,457
''where Sita, who returned safely
from the clutches of Ravana...''

1195
03:17:25,832 --> 03:17:30,166
''was forced to stand a test by fire
by her own husband, Rama!''

1196
03:17:31,672 --> 03:17:36,006
From Sita to Maithili
to Janki to Ramdulaari...

1197
03:17:36,276 --> 03:17:39,803
so many women are being
charred in vicious fires!

1198
03:17:40,414 --> 03:17:42,405
And they will continue
to burn in the future!

1199
03:17:42,883 --> 03:17:45,374
Because we do not feel
a sense of shame anymore!

1200
03:17:46,820 --> 03:17:50,688
Every trace of shame and
humanity is dead for us.

1201
03:17:52,492 --> 03:17:55,427
Proof is this man here!

1202
03:17:55,796 --> 03:17:59,095
He raped a mother.
And he set her on fire!

1203
03:17:59,433 --> 03:18:02,095
And you are today felicitating him
on this high platform!

1204
03:18:03,570 --> 03:18:06,869
Cut the melodrama!
...throw her out!

1205
03:18:07,374 --> 03:18:09,001
Haven't you heard? Get lost!

1206
03:18:38,739 --> 03:18:40,730
''Do not worry, sister.
We are with you.''

1207
03:18:40,874 --> 03:18:43,468
Yes! We are with you.
- So am l.

1208
03:18:43,744 --> 03:18:46,474
''We will stand testimony!
- Yes, sister...''

1209
03:18:46,747 --> 03:18:48,977
l will stand testimony
against my husband.

1210
03:18:50,083 --> 03:18:51,414
Step back... Move!

1211
03:18:51,752 --> 03:18:54,516
''You can't hold me in prison
for even seven hours, lnspector.''

1212
03:18:54,888 --> 03:18:56,879
l have connections
right to the top.

1213
03:19:16,777 --> 03:19:19,712
''l,...''

1214
03:19:22,449 --> 03:19:26,215
could you consider me worthy
of forgiveness?

1215
03:19:36,463 --> 03:19:39,125
l'm fortunate to have you
for my wife.

1216
03:19:47,874 --> 03:19:49,466
''Come, sit in my taxi.''

1217
03:19:51,545 --> 03:19:53,445
Treat it like your own car.
Please get in.

1218
03:19:53,747 --> 03:19:54,736
You...?

1219
03:19:55,749 --> 03:19:58,081
''l told you, l met him at the wedding!
- The biscuit-seller?''

1220
03:19:59,753 --> 03:20:03,018
l've given up all that.
l drive a cab in New York now.

1221
03:20:03,356 --> 03:20:05,153
''This is my husband, Raghu.
- Hello.''

1222
03:20:05,459 --> 03:20:07,154
Daughter or son?
- Daughter.

1223
03:20:07,494 --> 03:20:09,428
What have you named her?
- Ramdulaari.

1224
03:20:09,896 --> 03:20:12,421
Nice name.
- And nice to have met you too.

1225
03:20:12,766 --> 03:20:16,031
Here's a pass for the charity show
l'm doing. Make sure you come.

1226
03:20:16,770 --> 03:20:18,863
''Janki?
- My friend, she's a fabulous dancer.''

1227
03:20:19,206 --> 03:20:21,868
''One pass won't do, madam.
We're two of us.''

1228
03:20:22,209 --> 03:20:25,508
''Have you got married, you mean?
